trans-unit.source: Represents the exception thrown when a component cannot be granted a license.
trans-unit.target: Representerar den undantag uppstod när en komponent inte kan beviljas en licens.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ComponentModel.LicenseManager.Validate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method throws LicenseException when a component cannot obtain a valid license.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ComponentModel.LicenseManager.Validate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden genererar LicenseException när en komponent går inte att hämta en giltig licens.</xref:System.ComponentModel.LicenseManager.Validate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: This occurs when a component is either not licensed, or is licensed but cannot be granted a valid license.
trans-unit.target: Detta inträffar när en komponent antingen licensieras inte eller är licensierad men går inte att bevilja en giltig licens.

trans-unit.source: For more information on licensing, see [How to: License Components and Controls](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Mer information om licensiering finns [så här: licens komponenter och kontroller](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
